{
  "comment_text": {
    "sn17.32:1.3": "Contentment, love, and understanding. Note, “skillful root” may be expressed in the singular even though it is threefold (<a href='https://suttacentral.net/mn9/en/sujato#7.1'>MN 9:7.1</a>). "
